      "content": "<details type=\"reasoning\" done=\"true\" duration=\"3\">\n<summary>Thought for 3 seconds</summary>\n&gt; 用户需要一个复杂的Three.js应用，包含以下功能：\n&gt; 1. 使用粒子创建圣诞树（球体、正方体组成）\n&gt; 2. 全屏雪花效果\n&gt; 3. 辉光和光晕效果\n&gt; 4. 手势识别（握拳、张开、捏合）\n&gt; 5. 状态切换动画\n&gt; 6. 相机控制\n&gt; 7. 礼物放置功能\n&gt; \n&gt; 我需要：\n&gt; - 使用MediaPipe Hands进行手势识别\n&gt; - Three.js创建3D场景\n&gt; - EffectComposer添加后期处理效果（辉光）\n&gt; - 平滑的动画过渡\n&gt; \n&gt; 让我创建一个完整的单文件应用：\n</details>\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>手势控制圣诞树</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        body {\n            background: #0a0e1a;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n        }\n        #canvas {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100vw;\n            height: 100vh;\n        }\n        #video {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 10px;\n            right: 10px;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 150px;\n            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transform: scaleX(-1);\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n        #info {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 10px;\n            left: 10px;\n            color: white;\n            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n        #loading {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            z-index: 100;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"loading\">正在加载手势识别...</div>\n    <div id=\"info\">\n        <div><strong>🎄 手势控制圣诞树</strong></div>\n        <div>👊 握拳 - 聚合状态</div>\n        <div>🖐️ 张开 - 散开状态</div>\n        <div>🤏 捏合 - 放置礼物</div>\n    </div>\n    <video id=\"video\" autoplay playsinline></video>\n    <canvas id=\"canvas\"></canvas>\n\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/build/three.min.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/postprocessing/EffectComposer.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/postprocessing/RenderPass.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/postprocessing/UnrealBloomPass.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/shaders/CopyShader.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/shaders/LuminosityHighPassShader.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.150.0/examples/js/postprocessing/ShaderPass.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/hands/hands.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/camera_utils/camera_utils.js\"></script>\n\n    <script>\n        // ========== 场景设置 ==========\n        const scene = new THREE.Scene();\n        scene.fog = new THREE.FogExp2(0x0a0e1a, 0.02);\n\n        const camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(75, window.innerWidth / window.innerHeight, 0.1, 1000);\n        camera.position.set(0, 5, 20);\n        camera.lookAt(0, 5, 0);\n\n        const renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({ \n            canvas: document.getElementById('canvas'), \n            antialias: true,\n            alpha: true \n        });\n        renderer.setSize(window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight);\n        renderer.setPixelRatio(window.devicePixelRatio);\n        renderer.toneMapping = THREE.ACESFilmicToneMapping;\n        renderer.toneMappingExposure = 1.2;\n\n        // ========== 后期处理 - 辉光效果 ==========\n        const composer = new THREE.EffectComposer(renderer);\n        const renderPass = new THREE.RenderPass(scene, camera);\n        composer.addPass(renderPass);\n\n        const bloomPass = new THREE.UnrealBloomPass(\n            new THREE.Vector2(window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight),\n            1.5, // 强度\n            0.4, // 半径\n            0.85 // 阈值\n        );\n        composer.addPass(bloomPass);\n\n        // ========== 灯光 ==========\n        const ambientLight = new THREE.AmbientLight(0xffffff, 0.6);\n        scene.add(ambientLight);\n\n        const pointLight1 = new THREE.PointLight(0xffd700, 2, 50);\n        pointLight1.position.set(10, 10, 10);\n        scene.add(pointLight1);\n\n        const pointLight2 = new THREE.PointLight(0xff0000, 1.5, 50);\n        pointLight2.position.set(-10, 5, -10);\n        scene.add(pointLight2);\n\n        // ========== 圣诞树粒子 ==========\n        class ChristmasTree {\n            constructor() {\n                this.particles = [];\n                this.createTree();\n            }\n\n            createTree() {\n                const colors = [0x2d5016, 0x3d6b1f, 0xffd700, 0xff0000]; // 哑光绿、金属金、圣诞红\n                const geometries = [\n                    new THREE.SphereGeometry(0.3, 16, 16),\n                    new THREE.BoxGeometry(0.4, 0.4, 0.4)\n                ];\n\n                // 创建圣诞树形状\n                for (let layer = 0; layer < 15; layer++) {\n                    const y = layer * 0.8;\n                    const radius = Math.max(0.5, 6 - layer * 0.4);\n                    const count = Math.floor(radius * 8);\n\n                    for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {\n                        const angle = (i / count) * Math.PI * 2;\n                        const x = Math.cos(angle) * radius;\n                        const z = Math.sin(angle) * radius;\n\n                        const geometry = geometries[Math.floor(Math.random() * geometries.length)];\n                        const material = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({\n                            color: colors[Math.floor(Math.random() * colors.length)],\n                            emissive: colors[Math.floor(Math.random() * colors.length)],\n                            emissiveIntensity: 0.5,\n                            metalness: Math.random() > 0.7 ? 0.8 : 0.2,\n                            roughness: 0.4\n                        });\n\n                        const mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material);\n                        mesh.position.set(x, y, z);\n                        \n                        // 存储原始位置和随机散开位置\n                        mesh.userData.originalPos = new THREE.Vector3(x, y, z);\n                        mesh.userData.scatteredPos = new THREE.Vector3(\n                            (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40,\n                            Math.random() * 30,\n                            (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40\n                        );\n                        mesh.userData.currentPos = new THREE.Vector3(x, y, z);\n                        mesh.userData.velocity = new THREE.Vector3();\n\n                        scene.add(mesh);\n                        this.particles.push(mesh);\n                    }\n                }\n\n                // 顶部星星\n                const starGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(0.6, 16, 16);\n                const starMaterial = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({\n                    color: 0xffd700,\n                    emissive: 0xffd700,\n                    emissiveIntensity: 2,\n                    metalness: 1,\n                    roughness: 0.1\n                });\n                const star = new THREE.Mesh(starGeometry, starMaterial);\n                star.position.set(0, 12, 0);\n                star.userData.originalPos = new THREE.Vector3(0, 12, 0);\n                star.userData.scatteredPos = new THREE.Vector3(\n                    (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40,\n                    Math.random() * 30,\n                    (Math.random() - 0.5) * 40\n                );\n                star.userData.currentPos = new THREE.Vector3(0, 12, 0);\n                star.userData.velocity = new THREE.Vector3();\n                scene.add(star);\n                this.particles.push(star);\n            }\n\n            update(targetState) {\n                this.particles.forEach(particle => {\n                    const target = targetState === 'gathered' \n                        ? particle.userData.originalPos \n                        : particle.userData.scatteredPos;\n                    \n                    // 平滑插值\n                    particle.userData.currentPos.lerp(target, 0.05);\n                    particle.position.copy(particle.userData.currentPos);\n                    \n                    // 旋转动画\n                    particle.rotation.x += 0.01;\n                    particle.rotation.y += 0.01;\n                });\n            }\n        }\n\n        // ========== 雪花系统 ==========\n        class SnowSystem {\n            constructor() {\n                this.snowflakes = [];\n                this.createSnow();\n            }\n\n            createSnow() {\n                const geometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(0.1, 8, 8);\n                const material = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({\n                    color: 0xffffff,\n                    emissive: 0xffffff,\n                    emissiveIntensity: 0.8,\n                    transparent: true,\n                    opacity: 0.9\n                });\n\n                for (let i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n                    const mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material.clone());\n                    \n                    mesh.position.set(\n                        (Math.random() - 0.5) * 60,\n                        Math.random() * 40,\n                        (Math.random() - 0.5) * 60\n                    );\n\n                    mesh.userData.originalY = mesh.position.y;\n                    mesh.userData.speed = Math.random() * 0.02 + 0.01;\n                    mesh.userData.scatteredPos = new THREE.Vector3(\n                        (Math.random() - 0.5) * 80,\n                        Math.random() * 40,\n                        (Math.random() - 0.5) * 80\n                    );\n                    mesh.userData.currentPos = mesh.position.clone();\n                    mesh.userData.falling = true;\n\n                    scene.add(mesh);\n                    this.snowflakes.push(mesh);\n                }\n            }\n\n            update(targetState) {\n                this.snowflakes.forEach(snow => {\n                    if (targetState === 'falling') {\n                        // 下落状态\n                        snow.userData.currentPos.y -= snow.userData.speed;\n                        if (snow.userData.currentPos.y < -5) {\n                            snow.userData.currentPos.y = 40;\n                        }\n                        snow.userData.currentPos.x += Math.sin(Date.now() * 0.001 + snow.id) * 0.02;\n                    } else {\n                        // 散开状态\n                        snow.userData.currentPos.lerp(snow.userData.scatteredPos, 0.02);\n                    }\n                    \n                    snow.position.copy(snow.userData.currentPos);\n                });\n            }\n        }\n\n        // ========== 手势指示器 ==========\n        class HandIndicator {\n            constructor() {\n                const geometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(0.5, 16, 16);\n                const material = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({\n                    color: 0xffffff,\n                    emissive: 0xffffff,\n                    emissiveIntensity: 2,\n                    transparent: true,\n                    opacity: 0.8\n                });\n                this.mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material);\n                this.mesh.visible = false;\n                scene.add(this.mesh);\n            }\n\n            update(x, y, z, visible) {\n                this.mesh.visible = visible;\n                if (visible) {\n                    this.mesh.position.set(x, y, z);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // ========== 礼物系统 ==========\n        class Gift {\n            constructor(x, y, z) {\n                const geometry = new THREE.BoxGeometry(1, 1, 1);\n                const material = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({\n                    color: [0xff0000, 0xffd700, 0x00ff00][Math.floor(Math.random() * 3)],\n                    emissive: 0xffd700,\n                    emissiveIntensity: 0.5,\n                    metalness: 0.3,\n                    roughness: 0.7\n                });\n                this.mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material);\n                this.mesh.position.set(x, y, z);\n                this.createdAt = Date.now();\n                this.scale = 1;\n                scene.add(this.mesh);\n            }\n\n            update() {\n                const elapsed = (Date.now() - this.createdAt) / 1000;\n                if (elapsed > 10) {\n                    this.scale -= 0.02;\n                    this.mesh.scale.setScalar(Math.max(0, this.scale));\n                    return this.scale <= 0;\n                }\n                this.mesh.rotation.y += 0.02;\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            remove() {\n                scene.remove(this.mesh);\n            }\n        }\n\n        // ========== 初始化 ==========\n        const tree = new ChristmasTree();\n        const snow = new SnowSystem();\n        const handIndicator = new HandIndicator();\n        const gifts = [];\n\n        let currentState = 'gathered';\n        let currentSnowState = 'falling';\n        let lastPinchState = false;\n\n        // ========== 手势识别 ==========\n        const videoElement = document.getElementById('video');\n        let handDetected = false;\n        let handX = 0, handY = 0, handZ = 0;\n\n        function onResults(results) {\n            if (results.multiHandLandmarks && results.multiHandLandmarks.length > 0) {\n                const landmarks = results.multiHandLandmarks[0];\n                handDetected = true;\n\n                // 计算手心位置\n                const palm = landmarks[9];\n                handX = (palm.x - 0.5) * 40;\n                handY = (1 - palm.y) * 30;\n                handZ = -palm.z * 20;\n\n                // 检测手势\n                const gesture = detectGesture(landmarks);\n                \n                if (gesture === 'fist') {\n                    currentState = 'gathered';\n                    currentSnowState = 'falling';\n                } else if (gesture === 'open') {\n                    currentState = 'scattered';\n                    currentSnowState = 'scattered';\n                    \n                    // 根据手的移动调整相机\n                    camera.position.x += (handX * 0.3 - camera.position.x) * 0.05;\n                    camera.lookAt(0, 5, 0);\n                } else if (gesture === 'pinch') {\n                    if (!lastPinchState) {\n                        gifts.push(new Gift(handX, handY, handZ));\n                    }\n                    lastPinchState = true;\n                } else {\n                    lastPinchState = false;\n                }\n            } else {\n                handDetected = false;\n            }\n        }\n\n        function detectGesture(landmarks) {\n            // 计算手指间距离\n            const thumb = landmarks[4];\n            const index = landmarks[8];\n            const middle = landmarks[12];\n            const ring = landmarks[16];\n            const pinky = landmarks[20];\n            const wrist = landmarks[0];\n\n            // 拇指和食指距离（捏合检测）\n            const thumbIndexDist = Math.hypot(thumb.x - index.x, thumb.y - index.y);\n            \n            // 手指到手腕的距离\n            const fingerDists = [\n                Math.hypot(index.x - wrist.x, index.y - wrist.y),\n                Math.hypot(middle.x - wrist.x, middle.y - wrist.y),\n                Math.hypot(ring.x - wrist.x, ring.y - wrist.y),\n                Math.hypot(pinky.x - wrist.x, pinky.y - wrist.y)\n            ];\n\n            if (thumbIndexDist < 0.05) {\n                return 'pinch';\n            } else if (fingerDists.every(d => d < 0.15)) {\n                return 'fist';\n            } else if (fingerDists.every(d => d > 0.2)) {\n                return 'open';\n            }\n            return 'unknown';\n        }\n\n        const hands = new Hands({\n            locateFile: (file) => `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/hands/${file}`\n        });\n\n        hands.setOptions({\n            maxNumHands: 1,\n            modelComplexity: 1,\n            minDetectionConfidence: 0.5,\n            minTrackingConfidence: 0.5\n        });\n\n        hands.onResults(onResults);\n\n        const camera_init = new Camera(videoElement, {\n            onFrame: async () => {\n                await hands.send({ image: videoElement });\n            },\n            width: 640,\n            height: 480\n        });\n\n        camera_init.start().then(() => {\n            document.getElementById('loading').style.display = 'none';\n        });\n\n        // ========== 动画循环 ==========\n        function animate() {\n            requestAnimationFrame(animate);\n\n            tree.update(currentState);\n            snow.update(currentSnowState);\n            handIndicator.update(handX, handY, handZ, handDetected);\n\n            // 更新礼物\n            for (let i = gifts.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n                if (gifts[i].update()) {\n                    gifts[i].remove();\n                    gifts.splice(i, 1);\n                }\n            }\n\n            composer.render();\n        }\n\n        animate();\n\n        // ========== 窗口调整 ==========\n        window.addEventListener('resize', () => {\n            camera.aspect = window.innerWidth / window.innerHeight;\n            camera.updateProjectionMatrix();\n            renderer.setSize(window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight);\n            composer.setSize(window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight);\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n这个应用实现了所有要求的功能：\n\n## 🎄 核心特性\n\n1. **圣诞树粒子系统**\n   - 使用球体和正方体组成\n   - 哑光绿、金属金、圣诞红配色\n   - 分层螺旋结构 + 金色顶星\n\n2. **辉光效果**\n   - 使用 UnrealBloomPass 创建电影感辉光\n   - 所有元素都有发光材质\n\n3. **雪花系统**\n   - 500个发光雪花粒子\n   - 下落态：自然飘落动画\n   - 散开态：随机漂浮\n\n4. **手势控制**\n   - 👊 **握拳**：聚合状态\n   - 🖐️ **张开五指**：散开状态 + 相机跟随\n   - 🤏 **捏合**：放置礼物（10秒后消失）\n   - 白色辉光指示器显示手部位置\n\n5. **平滑过渡**\n   - 所有状态切换使用 lerp 插值\n   - 流畅的动画效果\n\n将代码保存为 `.html` 文件，在浏览器中打开即可体验！需要允许摄像头权限。"
    }
